sequenceDiagram
    participant Widget as TECSAFE IFrame
    participant SDK as Widget SDK
    participant ShopUI as Shop Frontend

    Widget->>SDK: Needs Article Name and Price
    SDK->>ShopUI: Emit InMessageRequestArticleInfo
    Note over ShopUI: Fetch product data via your API
    ShopUI-->>SDK: e.respond with OutMessageArticleInfo
    SDK-->>Widget: Provide info or null fallback
    Note over Widget: Widget renders product text
